(Xingyue Tavern)

127
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,710
Ma'am, where's my dish?

128
00:07:15,370 --> 00:07:16,740
Ma'am, where's my dish?

129
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,070
Coming right up.

130
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,420
Sorry about that.

131
00:07:22,300 --> 00:07:23,270
Sorry about that.

132
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:28,190
Seems like she's been possessed
since she came back.

133
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,710
When will Young Master Su return

134
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,430
from his business
in another province?

135
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:56,430
You need to eat something,
or you'll get worse.

136
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,350
I can't face Xinyue anymore.

137
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:12,670
Let's leave here.

138
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:14,760
Alright.

139
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:17,430
Wherever you go, I'll be with you.

140
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:21,840
But,

141
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,910
before we leave,

142
00:08:25,940 --> 00:08:27,790
I want to see Xinyue one last time.

143
00:08:37,300 --> 00:08:38,140
Xinyue?

144
00:08:40,260 --> 00:08:41,150
Xinyue.

145
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:45,630
What's wrong?

146
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,840
Yao,

147
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:55,230
I miss him so much.

148
00:08:56,260 --> 00:08:59,220
(Pharmacy)

149
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,430
Aren't you going in?

150
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:13,520
Let's go.

